<!doctype html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Your Proposal Has Been Approved! - <%= title %></title>
  </head>

  <body
    style="
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      padding: 20px;
    "
  >
    <div
      style="
        width: 100%;
        margin: 0 auto;
        max-width: 600px;
        background-color: #fff;
      "
    >
      <div style="text-align: center; padding: 30px">
        <img
          src="https://utfs.io/f/7569a78d-1118-40e6-a844-bfc5433fcb83-yko3op.png"
          alt="GFE Logo"
          style="max-width: 150px"
        />
      </div>
      <div
        style="
          width: calc(100% - 20px);
          height: 1px;
          background-color: #eee;
          margin: 0 10px;
        "
      ></div>

      <div
        style="
          padding: 20px;
          margin: auto;
          background-color: #fff;
          font-size: 10pt;
        "
      >
        <p>Hello, <%= name %></p>
        <p>
          Great news! After thorough review, we're thrilled to inform you that
          your proposal titled <a href="<%= link %>"><%= title %></a> has been
          approved. Your submission is now officially part of our community's
          agenda, and we're excited about the positive change it proposes to
          bring to our DAO.
        </p>

        <p>
          We appreciate the time, effort, and insight you've poured into your
          proposal. It's community members like you who drive our collective
          progress and innovation.
        </p>

        <p>
          Congratulations, and thank you for contributing to our community's
          growth!
        </p>

        <p>Thank you once again for your valuable contribution!</p>

        <p>
          Warm regards,<br />
          GFE Foundation Community
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
